              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-b51bc174-e1e3-41e4-9057-c58ba2381291');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "\n",

              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",

              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#  Create scatter plots to explore relationships between pairs of numeric variables.\n",
        "sns.scatterplot(data=df, x='ApplicantIncome', y='CoapplicantIncome')\n",
        "plt.title('Applicant Income vs CoapplicantIncome')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Applicant Income')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('CoapplicantIncome')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "sns.scatterplot(data=df, x='ApplicantIncome', y='LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.title('Applicant Income vs LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Applicant Income')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "sns.scatterplot(data=df, x='CoapplicantIncome', y='LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.title('Coapplicant Income vs LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('Coapplicant Income')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('LoanAmount')\n",
        "plt.grid(True)\n",
        "plt.show()"

      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**2.3 Multivariate Analysis**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "SvaCXL5CtRAd"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#  Perform a correlation analysis to identify relationships between numeric variables.\n",
        "correlation_matrix = df[numeric_colomn].corr()\n",
        "correlation_matrix"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 206
        },
        "id": "DYfYsF0tsGty",
        "outputId": "89f0b41b-2b64-442f-9c66-753d3bf8b67e"
      },
      "execution_count": 36,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "                   ApplicantIncome  CoapplicantIncome  LoanAmount  \\\n",
              "ApplicantIncome           1.000000          -0.084353    0.445695   \n",
              "CoapplicantIncome        -0.084353           1.000000    0.230355   \n",

              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-d86f8545-3b3e-480f-adad-80aba3f2d4c8');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",
